{"tid":1829434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［魚蛋革命］初二旺角見。","createTime":"2020-01-18T17:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T11:34:36.000Z","uid":116560,"like":90,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"cf8fd47770a30aec15cea3e937a4a0b33f56baf0","tid":1829434,"uid":116560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"記唔記得呢一批手足，當初，我地甚至未學識叫大家做手足，甚至互相割蓆，指責。<br />\n呢批手足無計較到，依然挺身企係大家前面。<br />\n因為呢一日，香港出現左大批政治犯。<br />\n我地緊隨一眾義士既腳步，2020.1.26，今年初二，旺角見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ezgyZzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FezgyZzo.jpg&h=c6be4b12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LqmnSUs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLqmnSUs.jpg&h=a5f608dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳柏洋\t襲警罪 監禁9個月<br />\n陳卓軒\t在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序行為監禁21日\t<br />\n陳宇基\t襲警罪\t監禁3個月\t<br />\n陳浩文\t襲擊致造成身體傷害罪\t18個月感化\t<br />\n許嘉琪 暴動罪\t 監禁3年\t<br />\n麥子晞 暴動罪\t 監禁3年\t<br />\n薛達榮\t暴動罪\t監禁3年\t<br />\n楊家倫\t暴動罪 縱火罪 \t監禁4年9個月<br />\n監禁4年3個月<br />\n楊子軒 暴動罪\t入教導所 監禁3年<br />\n羅浩彥 監禁3年<br />\n連潤發監禁3年<br />\n蘇德成\t刑事毀壞罪\t監禁4個月\t<br />\n鄧浩賢\t暴動罪\t監禁2年10個月\t<br />\n莫嘉濤\t兩項暴動罪 一項刑事損壞罪 一項襲警罪\t監禁4年3個月\t<br />\n鍾志華\t\t監禁3年9個月\t<br />\n何錦森\t\t監禁3年9個月\t<br />\n霍廷昊\t\t監禁3年8個月\t<br />\n陳和祥\t\t監禁3年5個月\t<br />\n鄧敬宗\t\t監禁3年6個月\t<br />\n李卓軒\t\t監禁2年9個月\t<br />\n林永旺\t\t監禁3年8個月\t<br />\n葉梓豐\t\t入教導所\t<br />\n吳挺愷\t\t監禁2年4個月\t<br />\n2018年6月\t盧建民\t暴動罪\t監禁7年\t<br />\n梁天琦\t暴動罪<br />\n襲警罪\t監禁6年<br />\n監禁1年\t同期執行<br />\n黃家駒\t暴動罪\t監禁3年6個月\t<br />\n容偉業\t暴動罪\t監禁3年\t<br />\n袁智駒\t暴動罪\t監禁3年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n毋忘魚蛋革命。<br />\n<br />\n2020.1.26 初二晚七時旺角見。<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立。"},{"pid":"c52caf37349a408a3e7566a9170faca9acf9cb33","tid":1829434,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T17:35:12.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">（1）</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n19/1/2020 （ 22000 人）<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>新白宮聯署：<br />\n計劃香港雙普選</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1D2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=c1220756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan</a><br />\n<br />\n快啲簽爆佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">（2）</code></pre><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n同場推呢個<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">18歲生日快樂 即刻登記做選民\n只要在2020年7月25日或以前年滿18歲，今年5月2日前可登記做選民</code></pre><br />\n地方選區選民新登記申請表：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1D2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=0037d64a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf</span></span>"},{"pid":"b8dea976734ab7f60680c07fb8fa23861b94feb5","tid":1829434,"uid":64514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T17:41:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71c8ab21b5c790036003e8b12cc433309ecd3c4","tid":1829434,"uid":76310,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T17:43:00.000Z","msg":"接近三十個義士坐冤獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be60